appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Official Bunpro companion app. Still in development.

Tapping on vocab/grammar anywhere will open grammar point.
Adjusted writeup UI to look more like on website.
Change dashboard SRS levels to match new level naming conventions and make them clickable to see a breakdown of each.
Fixed minor bugs ( Vacation mode toggle ).
Adjusted report a bug function to provide info about current version.

- Native reviews: Now you can review your grammar/vocab natively, instead of via a webview. Accessible via the hamburger menu.
- Faster downloading
- Reset data button
- Smoother animations
- Add data download indicators
- Fixed the issue when Chinese font was used instead of Japanese one, which was especially problematic for some characters
- make the text more even
- numerous other bugs fixed

fixed the bug crashing native reviews
progress bars are now multi-colored
fixed the gray box appearing instead of the app icon on the notification prompt
fixed font inconsistencies across the app
the review forecast chart has been added
the past reviews chart has been added
to access the charts, you have to drag the user information section on the dashboard screen
fixed the bug when Japanese input did not work correctly with Japanese keyboards
some minor bugs and UI fixes

* Added Japanese language support
You can change the app language in settings.

* Added Color accent support
The support of the blue accent mode.

* Native reviews
Native reviews are now the default reviewing functionality

* Added male voice support
It is now possible to choose between a male and female speaker

**Other changes and bug fixes**
* native reviews: fixed a bug when some reviews persisted & a bug when one review remained unfinished
* various bug and performance fixes

* Added Native Study Support
You can now use the study functionality natively.

* Added Vertical Reading Mode
You can now read reading passages vertically.

* Flashcard mode
Flashcard mode is now supported for vocabulary.

* Split reviews
It is now possible to review vocabulary and grammar separately.

**Other changes and bug fixes**
* the downloading indicator has been added to the dashboard screen to notify whenever data is downloading
* various bug and performance fixes

- fixed vacation mode not working properly
- fixed ghost reviews number not displaying correctly
- fixed html tags showing sometimes under example sentences
- fixed rare bug when readings displayed grey screen
fixes a rare bug when data never downloads completely
